<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Author-Books</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,400,500,700&display=swap">
    <style>
        /* Basic styles for the page */
        body, html {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%; /* Set the height to 100% to cover the entire viewport */
            background-image: url("/public/bg.jpg"); /* Gray gradient */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            color: #fff;
        }

        h1{
            color: black;
        }

        /* Navigation bar styles */
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: rgb(0, 49, 128);
            padding: 10px;
        }

        /* Logo and website name */
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Navigation links */
        .nav-links {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
        }

        .nav-links li {
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Main content container */
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
			padding-top: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); /* Semi-transparent background */
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Additional information section */
        .info-section {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: black;
        }

        /* Button styles */
        .login-button, .signup-button {
            background-color: rgb(0, 66, 128);
            color: #00aeff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .login-button:hover, .signup-button:hover {
            background-color: rgb(0, 4, 255);
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">Author-Books</div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="/login" class="login-button">Login</a></li>
            <li><a href="/signup" class="signup-button">SignUp</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <br><br>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Author-Books</h1>
        <div class="info-section">
            <p>The Author and Books Search Engine is a powerful online tool designed to help users discover and explore a vast collection of literary works and their respective authors. With a user-friendly interface, it allows enthusiasts to search for authors, their biographies, and comprehensive lists of their published books. Whether you're an avid reader, a researcher, or simply curious, this search engine is your gateway to the world of literature, making it easy to find and learn about your favorite authors and the literary treasures they've created.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
